Hanyang University OOP Class Lecture Note This site is made for &ldquo;COM2018: Object-Oriented Programming&rdquo; class in order to organize codes from lectures.
Currently Organized Lectures&hellip;
Lecture 1. Course Introduction &amp; Java Basics Lecture 2. Classes and Objects, Static, Types Lecture 3. Defining &amp; Instantiating, Static vs Non-static, Managing - Complexity, Primitive Types Lecture 4. Unit Testing Lecture 5. Linked List (IntList &amp; SLList), PUBLIC VS PRIVATE, Nested Classes, List &amp; Array Lecture 6. Doubly Linked List, Generic Lists, AList Lecture 7. Inheritance and Interface, Overriding and Overloading Ongoing &hellip;
